&gt;
&gt; 
&gt;  Thanks for listening. Yeah, that&#39;s the problem with noise 
reduction methods, they tend to take out voices. I think if I used 
the muffled sound consistently they would talk through it though, the 
goal being to get higher level voices, and audio.  The clarifier is 
just a low pass filter that can be adjusted--just an idea.
&gt;  I have some female guides that speak sometimes, and there&#39;s the 
seven sisters that come though sometimes, but I don&#39;t know much about 
that. 
