&gt; By the way, I did listen to your tone control clip. Since I&#39;m new 
to this my comments are probably not &quot;worth&quot; much at this point. I 
thought the entire clip itself was a lot smoother and clearer than 
most I&#39;ve heard so far from various sources (the mixed station sounds 
are in smaller pieces so for someone like me it would be easier to 
pick out the EVPs as opposed to entire words from radio announcers). 
The short piece about 2/3 of the way through, where I&#39;m guessing you 
used a clarifier, sounded muffled to me, which makes me think it 
would also muffle the EVPs. Definitely easier on the ears but for 
someone inexperienced (and I seem to be the only one here!) it seems 
it would be harder to pick out the real words too.
&gt; 
